[2] Outbreak summary
Date: Thu 25 Jul 2019
Source: Actualite [in French, trans. Corr.SB, abridged, edited]
https://actualite.cd/2019/07/25/rdc-ebola-2-592-cas-et-1-743-deces-un-taux-de-letalite-de-67


DRC-Ebola: 2592 cases and 1743 deaths, a case-fatality rate of 67%
--------------------
The Ebola epidemic has now reached 2592 cases and 1743 deaths. This represents a case-fatality rate of 67%, the World Health Organization announced Wed 24 Jul 2019 (WHO). The same source reports that 56% of cases with known age and sex are women and 28% of children under 18 years of age.

An increase in cases compared to last week was also reported, even among health staff, with 4 new infections.

Since August 2018, a total of 171 502 people have been vaccinated.

